<br>
Somone asked me recently if Fed was big enuff to take down Vindi yet hehe... - no, it isn't.... but killing Doomshade is a good way to learn how to do a mob like that.<br>
<br>
Some info:<br>
<br>
Doomshade quads for 450's, has devastating flurry's, 150k hp's, is hard to spawn, hard to pull, and often quite hard to trigger, as u can only trigger it once every 3-4 days real time.<br>
<br>
She drops weapons, Int caster stuff, and, more importantly, lvl 60 Luclin spells - such as Blessing of Aego, and C3.<br>
<br>
I can't post this as a raid because, as i said, it's often killed as soon as the trigger is ready but one day, when there is enough Fed peeps online to try it, and i notice the trigger is up and no uber-guilds are on the way, I would like to gather a force to try it.<br>
